resources.description: With the rapid development of computer technology, computer networks have become an important part of human society, and have brought huge effect into the social development. It used a variety of database technology, which gave hackers one way to attack. Thus, the paper analyzed related problem aiming at threat and prevention of the computer network database.
resources.name: Attack and Defense of Computer Network Database
